fields.name: Beginner box
fields.description: A plant box subscription for beginners. Contains 1 medium and 2 small sized plants.

fields.name: ZZ plant
fields.description: Perfect for the shady corner or hallway, this plant thrives with little to no sunlight. Since it's so durable it a perfect fit for the beginner planter.

fields.name: Small parlour palm
fields.description: A small and palm with beautiful foliage. Likes semi-shade and a moit enviroment.

fields.name: Potting soil
fields.description: A great versitile potting soil for most plants. Contains perlite, compost,coco-fiber, charcoal and a small dosage of fertilizer.

fields.name: Small green glazed pot
fields.description: A lovely and small pot. It's green wit ha light green speckle on the top and bottom of the pot.

fields.name: Golden watering can
fields.description: Beautiful and modern watering can in metal. Holds 1 litre of water.

fields.name: Lace aloe
fields.description: Finally we have aloes in the shop! This small, prickly and green aloe is a easily cared for aloe. It dosen't require alot of attention and keeps its beautiful colors and leaves all year.
